{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Banyak Adegan Penuh Aksi di Film Thor: Ragnarok","content":"<p>Guys, bersiaplah menyambut tayangan perdana film produksi Marvel Studios, Thor: Ragnarok di bioskop kesayanganmu pada tanggal 25 Oktober 2017 mendatang.</p>\n<p>Ditemui di sela-sela syuting film di Queensland, Australia belum lama ini, Chris Hemsworth menceritakan lebih banyak detail mengenai film ini. Ia menegaskan bahwa Â film Thor: Ragnarok bukanlah kelanjutan dari nasib Thor di Avengers: Age of Ultron. Film ini juga mempunyai durasi yang cukup singkat dibandingkan film Marvel Studios lainnya yakni hanya 1 jam 40 menit.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22938\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22938\" data-attachment-id=\"22938\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/attachment/isi-1-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : m.zimbio.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : m.zimbio.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22938\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-1.jpg\" alt=\"(from : m.zimbio.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22938\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : m.zimbio.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Chris bercerita, di film Thor: Ragnarok, Thor tengah dalam perjalanan untuk mencari identitasnya sendiri. Ia berasal dari Asgard, tetapi kemudian menjadi raja dan tinggal di bumi. Namun tetap saja ia tak berasal dari bumi dan ia merasa tak cocok berada di sana. Thor pun kemudian pergi untuk mencari jawaban atas asal usulnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22941\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22941\" data-attachment-id=\"22941\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/attachment/isi-2-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : nerdist.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : nerdist.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22941\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-2.jpg\" alt=\"(from : nerdist.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22941\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : nerdist.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di tengah perjalanannya tersebut, Thor malah dipertemukan dengan kekacauan akibat seorang penjahat yang melepaskan diri. Thor dihadapkan dengan musuh baru yakni Hela (diperankan oleh aktris Cate Blanchett), yang hendak membawa kehancuran pada tempat tinggalnya. Hela disebut sebagai dewi kematian dan penguasa dari Hel dan Niflheim. Hela sendiri memiliki dendam terhadap ayah Thor, Odin, karena telah memenjarakannya selama beribu-ribu tahun. Dengan kehadiran penjahat baru yang mengancam keberadaan Asgard tersebut, Thor pun mengumpulkan rekan lama dan baru untuk mengalahkan Hela serta menghentikan Ragnarok.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22944\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22944\" data-attachment-id=\"22944\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/attachment/isi-3-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : toofab.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : toofab.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22944\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-3.jpg\" alt=\"(from : toofab.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22944\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : toofab.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Thor juga diasingkan ke planet lain tanpa palu Mjolnir sampai dirinya harus mengikuti pertandingan agar bisa kembali ke Asgard dan menghentikan Ragnarok, yakni sebutan untuk kehancuran dan berakhirnya peradaban Asgard di tangan Hela yang kejam. Dalam film yang diproduksi oleh Kevin Feige ini, Thor akan berjumpa kembali dengan rekannya di Avengers, The Incredible Hulk (diperankan oleh Mark Ruffalo). Terlihat dari <em>trailer</em> film yang telah dirilis, keduanya dipertemukan di semacam arena bertarung gladiator.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22947\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22947\" data-attachment-id=\"22947\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/attachment/isi-4-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : uproxx.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : uproxx.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22947\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-4.jpg\" alt=\"(from : uproxx.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22947\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : uproxx.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Selain itu saat diwawancarai, Chris Hemsworth mengaku banyak menemui perubahan adegan film. Tak hanya dituntut perubahan fisik, ia pun banyak dihadapkan dengan adegan penuh aksi di sini. Chris menjelaskan jika ia harus banyak berlatih untuk melakukan adegan aksi tersebut. Karena setelah kehilangan palunya, Thor pun mau tak mau harus menggunakan senjata yang berbeda untuk menghadapi musuh. Thor diharuskan untuk menggunakan senjata lain seperti pedang, tembakan laser, hingga senjata-senjata lain.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22950\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22950\" data-attachment-id=\"22950\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/attachment/isi-5-19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : screenrant.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : screenrant.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22950\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-5.jpg\" alt=\"(from : screenrant.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22950\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : screenrant.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sementara untuk latihan fisik, Chris Hemsworth tak begitu mengalami banyak perubahan. Begitu juga dengan menu dietnya sehari-hari untuk membentuk tubuh Thor. Dirinya hanya harus makan banyak makanan dengan benar dan banyak berlatih. Chris bahkan harus menghabiskan waktu berjam-jam di <em>gym</em> untuk membentuk tubuh Thor yang sangat atletis itu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22953\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22953\" data-attachment-id=\"22953\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/banyak-adegan-penuh-aksi-di-film-thor-ragnarok/attachment/isi-6-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : moviepilot.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : moviepilot.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22953\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ISI-6-1.jpg\" alt=\"(from : moviepilot.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22953\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : moviepilot.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Oiya di film ini, dua kakak-beradik Thor dan Loki (diperankan oleh Tom Hiddleston) kembali mewarnai jalan cerita film Thor : Ragnarok. Akting antara keduanya biasanya memberi sentuhan humor yang bikin kalian ngakak guys. Duh, jadi ga sabar ya pengen segera nonton filmnya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"0831b89a-b08f-5017-b367-89c078f8eb32"}}}